<article id="post-129224" class="post-129224 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-armageddon-scenarios category-conspiracy-fact-and-theory category-controlling-the-herd category-editors-choice category-featuredreports category-general category-headlines category-news category-news-headlines category-perspectives category-survival-and-preparedness category-videos tag-annihilation tag-asteroid tag-earth-leveling-event tag-ele tag-meteor tag-military tag-nasa tag-space-rocks">
