<article id="post-129196" class="post-129196 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-armageddon-scenarios category-conspiracy-fact-and-theory category-controlling-the-herd category-crimepolice-state category-editors-choice category-featuredreports category-general category-headlines category-media-and-propaganda category-news-headlines category-people category-perspectives category-politics category-resistance-headlines category-war-and-conflict tag-conspiracies tag-false-flags tag-government tag-lies tag-mass-shootings tag-matrix tag-propaganda tag-psyop tag-reality tag-sandy-hook">
